# Load Ledgers V5 — security response headers for Cloudflare Pages.
#
# BEARDS DOCTRINE — Truth as Architecture: security is enforced at the edge on
# every response, not left to chance. These headers are what the Mozilla HTTP
# Observatory grades. Applied to every path on the site.
#
# WHAT EACH HEADER DOES (and which Observatory test it fixes):
#   Strict-Transport-Security : forces HTTPS for 2 years, eligible for preload.   (HSTS test)
#   Content-Security-Policy   : whitelists exactly what the app may load/connect. (CSP test)
#   X-Frame-Options + frame-ancestors 'none' : blocks clickjacking / embedding.   (X-Frame-Options test)
#   X-Content-Type-Options    : already passing; kept here so it never regresses.
#   Referrer-Policy           : already passing; kept explicit.
#   Permissions-Policy        : disables APIs the app never uses (camera mic etc).
#
# CSP NOTE: the allow-list below is built for what loadledgers ACTUALLY uses —
# its own origin, Google Fonts, the ledger-v5 Worker API, and the PDF.js library
# served from cdnjs.cloudflare.com. PDF.js is required to render PDF BOLs and PDF
# receipts to canvas before scanning; without cdnjs in script-src AND worker-src
# (PDF.js spawns its own web worker, pdf.worker.min.js) the browser blocks the
# library and every PDF upload silently fails. If a future feature loads from a
# new origin, that origin must be added here or it will be blocked. 'unsafe-inline'
# is included for style/script because the app and the static pages use inline
# styles and small inline scripts; removing it later (via hashes/nonces) would
# raise the grade further but is not required for A.

/*
  Strict-Transport-Security: max-age=63072000; includeSubDomains; preload
  Content-Security-Policy: default-src 'self'; script-src 'self' 'unsafe-inline' https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com; worker-src 'self' blob: https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com; style-src 'self' 'unsafe-inline' https://fonts.googleapis.com; font-src 'self' https://fonts.gstatic.com; img-src 'self' data: blob: https://ledger-v5.d49rwgmpj9.workers.dev; connect-src 'self' https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com https://ledger-v5.d49rwgmpj9.workers.dev; frame-ancestors 'none'; base-uri 'self'; form-action 'self'; object-src 'none'
  X-Frame-Options: DENY
  X-Content-Type-Options: nosniff
  Referrer-Policy: strict-origin-when-cross-origin
  Permissions-Policy: geolocation=(), microphone=(), camera=(), payment=()
